1
00:01:49,443 --> 00:01:50,569
[Robotnik] Doctor's log.

2
00:01:50,653 --> 00:01:53,030
It's day 243 in this...

3
00:01:54,073 --> 00:01:55,491
portobello purgatory.

4
00:01:56,826 --> 00:01:59,245
My only companion is a rock I named Stone.

5
00:02:02,456 --> 00:02:06,168
The question is,
for whom am I narrating this?

6
00:02:06,836 --> 00:02:07,837
[shudders]

7
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:11,757
<i>It seems I've become a featured player
in the theater of the absurd.</i>

8
00:02:11,841 --> 00:02:14,969
<i>Marooned in deep space
by that wretched blue rodent.</i>

9
00:02:15,052 --> 00:02:16,762
<i>But it's all good,</i>

10
00:02:16,846 --> 00:02:19,598
<i>thanks to a breathable atmosphere
and my supreme intellect,</i>

11
00:02:19,682 --> 00:02:22,935
<i>sharpened against the only competitor
savvy enough to bring it.</i>

12
00:02:23,019 --> 00:02:24,437
Chanterelle to d4.

13
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,521
Mmm.

14
00:02:25,604 --> 00:02:28,774
<i>I've been striving to make fungi into
a functional drink of choice...</i>

15
00:02:28,858 --> 00:02:30,276
[sniffs] Mushroom coffee.

16
00:02:30,359 --> 00:02:31,360
[slurps]

17
00:02:31,444 --> 00:02:32,695
[sputters, gags]

18
00:02:32,778 --> 00:02:34,447
<i>...with limited...</i>

19
00:02:35,823 --> 00:02:36,991
<i>limited...</i>

20
00:02:37,074 --> 00:02:38,659
[gags, coughs]

21
00:02:38,743 --> 00:02:40,202
<i>...limited...</i>

22
00:02:40,995 --> 00:02:42,246
<i>success.</i>

23
00:02:44,457 --> 00:02:45,624
[gasps]

24
00:02:45,708 --> 00:02:48,544
<i>But today, day243,</i>

25
00:02:48,627 --> 00:02:51,839
<i>has brought a new optimism
to my most pressing endeavor...</i>

26
00:02:51,922 --> 00:02:56,635
<i>planetus exodus to returnicus
and kick blue butticus.</i>

27
00:03:03,601 --> 00:03:05,394
If my calculations are correct,

28
00:03:05,478 --> 00:03:08,105
and there's no reason to say "if"
because they always are...

29
00:03:09,523 --> 00:03:13,319
this quill is going to power
my masterpiece.

30
00:03:15,613 --> 00:03:16,989
Let's light this candle...

31
00:03:18,699 --> 00:03:21,410
- and see who comes a-knockin'.
- [electricity crackling]

32
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:25,831
[shrieks]

33
00:04:27,101 --> 00:04:28,310
- Greetings!
- [gasps]

34
00:04:32,064 --> 00:04:34,191
[screaming]

35
00:04:34,275 --> 00:04:36,527
<i>Klaatu barada nikto.</i>

36
00:04:38,737 --> 00:04:40,322
[screams]

37
00:04:43,075 --> 00:04:45,619
[weapons humming]

38
00:04:46,912 --> 00:04:48,789
Agent Stone? Now!

39
00:04:52,751 --> 00:04:55,337
[yells, grunts]

40
00:04:58,966 --> 00:05:00,009
[Robotnik] Thank you, Stone.

41
00:05:02,052 --> 00:05:06,682
It's time to say goodbye to
this piece-of-shiitake planet!

42
00:05:07,475 --> 00:05:08,767
[grunts]

43
00:05:08,851 --> 00:05:11,061
[panting]

44
00:05:16,192 --> 00:05:17,735
Huh?

45
00:05:31,874 --> 00:05:33,626
Where did you get that?

46
00:05:37,463 --> 00:05:40,132
From a little blue menace
on the planet called Earth.

47
00:05:42,718 --> 00:05:44,929
I'd be happy to show you the way.

48
00:06:07,868 --> 00:06:09,745
[chuckles] Oh.

49
00:06:09,828 --> 00:06:12,414
[engine racing]

50
00:06:12,498 --> 00:06:14,792
[sirens wailing]

51
00:06:19,672 --> 00:06:20,881
They're still on us.

52
00:06:21,924 --> 00:06:23,592
This'll slow 'em down. [grunts]

53
00:06:23,676 --> 00:06:24,802
[tires screeching]

54
00:06:36,397 --> 00:06:37,982
["It's Tricky" playing]

55
