416
00:23:11,307 --> 00:23:14,686
Sonic, meet Knuckles.

417
00:23:14,769 --> 00:23:16,980
My new BFFAE.

418
00:23:17,063 --> 00:23:20,441
Bestest friend forever and ever!

419
00:23:20,525 --> 00:23:23,653
Look, Robotnik, I don't care
who you brought to help you.

420
00:23:23,736 --> 00:23:25,572
You're never going to get my power.

421
00:23:25,655 --> 00:23:28,241
Do I look like I need your power?

422
00:23:28,908 --> 00:23:31,077
[both yelling]

423
