[grunts]

424
00:23:38,793 --> 00:23:42,255
So nice when diabolical evil
lives up to the hype.

425
00:23:42,338 --> 00:23:43,631
[groaning]

426
00:23:43,715 --> 00:23:45,925
[grunts]

427
00:23:46,009 --> 00:23:47,343
Where is it?

428
00:23:47,427 --> 00:23:50,471
Oh, you want it? Here it comes.

429
00:23:50,555 --> 00:23:53,850
I was expecting more of you.

430
00:23:53,933 --> 00:23:55,184
You're unskilled.

431
00:23:56,019 --> 00:23:57,312
Untrained.

432
00:23:58,855 --> 00:24:01,190
And unworthy!

433
00:24:02,650 --> 00:24:05,945
You forgot one. Unstoppable.

434
00:24:11,576 --> 00:24:13,578
[energy crackling]

435
00:24:21,711 --> 00:24:23,880
[yelling]

436
00:24:28,635 --> 00:24:29,927
[groaning]

437
00:24:32,138 --> 00:24:35,975
It is my destiny to do
what my ancestors could not...

438
00:24:36,059 --> 00:24:40,229
to restore the ultimate power
to the home of my people.

439
00:24:41,022 --> 00:24:42,148
[Sonic] Ultimate power?

440
00:24:42,231 --> 00:24:44,776
I don't know what you're talking about.

441
00:24:44,859 --> 00:24:46,069
You've got the wrong guy.

442
00:24:46,152 --> 00:24:48,321
Ultimate power?

443
00:24:48,404 --> 00:24:51,616
Now you're speaking my language.

444
00:24:51,699 --> 00:24:54,786
Don't play dumb with me,
apprentice of Longclaw.

445
00:24:54,869 --> 00:24:56,496
You knew Longclaw?

446
00:24:56,579 --> 00:24:57,914
Longclaw and her people

447
00:24:57,997 --> 00:25:00,625
were the sworn enemy of my tribe,
the Echidna.

448
00:25:00,708 --> 00:25:02,960
We fought and died at their hands,

449
00:25:03,044 --> 00:25:05,713
and now you will die at mine.

450
00:25:05,797 --> 00:25:07,965
[siren wailing]

451
00:25:10,968 --> 00:25:12,387
[grunts]

452
00:25:13,805 --> 00:25:16,307
[imitating electric servo motors]

453
00:25:16,391 --> 00:25:18,559
Come on. Get in! I'm on your side.

454
00:25:18,643 --> 00:25:20,561
I'm sorry. Who are you?

455
00:25:20,645 --> 00:25:21,729
[groaning]

456
00:25:21,813 --> 00:25:23,523
You know what? It doesn't matter.

457
00:25:23,606 --> 00:25:24,607
[grunts]

458
00:25:24,691 --> 00:25:25,983
[both scream]

459
00:25:26,067 --> 00:25:28,069
[Sonic] Get us out of here! Go, go, go!

460
00:25:28,152 --> 00:25:29,445
[tires squealing]

461
00:25:29,529 --> 00:25:31,698
[grunting, snarling]

462
00:25:31,781 --> 00:25:33,324
