463
00:25:33,408 --> 00:25:35,493
- [growling]
- [whimpering]

464
00:25:35,576 --> 00:25:36,994
Gross! Is he licking it?

465
00:25:38,204 --> 00:25:39,497
See ya!

466
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:41,874
[Sonic] Make sure
to get your shots, Eggman!

467
00:25:42,792 --> 00:25:45,586
[panting]

468
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:49,298
[Sonic] Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

469
00:25:49,382 --> 00:25:50,758
Whoa!

470
00:25:52,510 --> 00:25:53,886
[yelling]

471
00:25:55,763 --> 00:25:57,348
Wow. Okay. Let me just say

472
00:25:57,432 --> 00:25:59,434
